name: Florida State Art Print 8x10 CHOOSE YOUR COLOR
description:
State Art Print - Florida

Featuring the flamingo and one of the many various types of fish that Florida is blessed to have, as well as the being one of the leading producer of citrus fruit in the states. Is this the state that steals your heart?

Print measures 8" x 10" and is printed professionally on Kodak Professional Endura Linen paper for a beautiful texture. 

Your print will arrive in high resolution, watermark removed, and carefully packed in a clear sleeve with a chipboard backing and sturdy mailer.

Choose your color from 9 choices: Red, Orange, Yellow, Green, Blue, Purple, Brown, Grey and Black. Please see second and third photo examples of color choices. 
***Please keep in mind monitor colors can vary*** If no color is selected, you will receive the color shown in first photo.

Each print is an original piece of artwork. Copyright belongs to the artist, and does not transfer in any way.
